---
import CaseStudyLayout from '../layouts/CaseStudyLayout.astro';
---

<CaseStudyLayout
  title="Truist — Digital Banking Platform"
  description="How I built and scaled a 30-person design org at SunTrust across all lines of business, then led business and commercial banking design through the $66B merger to Truist."
  ogImage="/images/truist/1771246115132-cd678175.png"
>

<style>
  :root {
    --truist-purple: #3B1A5A;
    --truist-deep: #2D1446;
    --truist-teal: #00B4A0;
    --warm-white: #F7F5F2;
    --soft-purple: #F3EFF8;
    --text-primary: #1A1A1A;
    --text-secondary: #5A5A5A;
    --text-light: rgba(255,255,255,0.85);
    --accent: #3B1A5A;
  }

  /* ── Hero ── */
  .hero {
    position: relative;
    min-height: 100vh;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--truist-deep) 0%, var(--truist-purple) 50%, #5A2D82 100%);
    overflow: hidden;
    padding: 120px 80px;
  }

  .hero::before {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    top: -30%;
    right: -10%;
    width: 700px;
    height: 700px;
    border-radius: 50%;
    background: radial-gradient(circle, rgba(0,180,160,0.12) 0%, transparent 70%);
    pointer-events: none;
  }

  .hero-left {
    flex: 1;
    max-width: 600px;
    z-index: 1;
  }

  .hero-right {
    flex: 1;
    display: flex;
    justify-content: center;
    align-items: center;
    z-index: 1;
  }

  .hero-right img {
    max-height: 600px;
    width: auto;
    border-radius: 24px;
    box-shadow: 0 40px 80px rgba(0,0,0,0.4);
  }

  .hero-label {
    font-size: 13px;
    font-weight: 500;
    letter-spacing: 3px;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--truist-teal);
    margin-bottom: 24px;
  }

  .hero-title {
    font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif;
    font-size: clamp(40px, 5vw, 68px);
    font-weight: 400;
    color: #fff;
    line-height: 1.1;
    margin-bottom: 28px;
  }

  .hero-subtitle {
    font-size: 18px;
    font-weight: 300;
    color: var(--text-light);
    line-height: 1.8;
    max-width: 500px;
  }

  /* ── Ecosystem Strip ── */
  .ecosystem {
    background: var(--soft-purple);
    padding: 120px 80px;
  }

  .ecosystem-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
    gap: 32px;
    margin-top: 64px;
    max-width: 1400px;
  }

  .eco-card {
    background: #fff;
    border-radius: 16px;
    overflow: hidden;
    box-shadow: 0 4px 24px rgba(59,26,90,0.06);
    transition: transform 0.35s ease, box-shadow 0.35s ease;
  }

  .eco-card:hover {
    transform: translateY(-6px);
    box-shadow: 0 20px 48px rgba(59,26,90,0.12);
  }

  .eco-card img {
    width: 100%;
    display: block;
  }

  .eco-card-text {
    padding: 24px 28px;
  }

  .eco-card-text h3 {
    font-size: 17px;
    font-weight: 500;
    color: var(--text-primary);
    margin-bottom: 6px;
  }

  .eco-card-text p {
    font-size: 14px;
    font-weight: 300;
    color: var(--text-secondary);
    line-height: 1.6;
  }

  /* ── Dark showcase ── */
  .showcase-dark {
    background: var(--truist-deep);
    padding: 120px 80px;
  }

  .showcase-dark .section-label { color: var(--truist-teal); }
  .showcase-dark .section-heading { color: #fff; }
  .showcase-dark .section-body { color: var(--text-light); }

  .showcase-row {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    gap: 48px;
    margin-top: 64px;
    max-width: 1400px;
  }

  .showcase-card {
    border-radius: 12px;
    overflow: hidden;
    background: rgba(255,255,255,0.04);
    border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.06);
    transition: transform 0.35s ease;
  }

  .showcase-card:hover {
    transform: translateY(-4px);
  }

  .showcase-card img {
    width: 100%;
    display: block;
  }

  .showcase-card-text {
    padding: 24px 28px;
  }

  .showcase-card-text h3 {
    font-size: 17px;
    font-weight: 500;
    color: #fff;
    margin-bottom: 4px;
  }

  .showcase-card-text p {
    font-size: 14px;
    font-weight: 300;
    color: rgba(255,255,255,0.5);
  }

  /* ── Wealth / Enterprise ── */
  .wealth {
    background: var(--warm-white);
  }

  .wealth-hero-img {
    margin-top: 64px;
    border-radius: 16px;
    overflow: hidden;
    box-shadow: 0 8px 40px rgba(0,0,0,0.08);
    max-width: 1400px;
  }

  .wealth-hero-img img {
    width: 100%;
    display: block;
  }

  /* ── Responsive ── */
  @media (max-width: 1024px) {
    .hero { flex-direction: column; padding: 80px 32px; gap: 48px; text-align: center; }
    .hero-left { max-width: 100%; }
    .hero-subtitle { max-width: 100%; }
    .hero-right img { max-height: 400px; }
    .ecosystem-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
    .ecosystem { padding: 80px 32px; }
    .showcase-dark { padding: 80px 32px; }
    .showcase-row { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
  }
</style>

  <!-- Hero -->
  <div class="hero">
    <div class="hero-left">
      <div class="hero-label">Truist Financial</div>
      <h1 class="hero-title">Defining the Digital Experience for America's 7th Largest Bank</h1>
      <p class="hero-subtitle">I built and scaled a 30-person design organization at SunTrust — owning every line of business — then led business and commercial banking design through the largest bank merger since 2008.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="hero-right">
      <img src="/images/truist/truist-mobile-app-tour-620x1150.jpg" alt="Truist mobile app screens">
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- Context -->
  <section class="context">
    <div class="context-inner">
      <div>
        <div class="section-label">The Challenge</div>
        <h2 class="section-heading">Two legacy banks became one. The digital experience had to earn that trust from day one.</h2>
        <p class="section-body">I inherited a small, nascent UX team at SunTrust with no research function, no UI practice, and no independent design voice. I scaled it to a 30-person multidisciplinary organization covering consumer, small business, wealth management, and commercial banking. When the $66B merger with BB&T created Truist, I led business and commercial banking design through the transition — rebuilding product experiences for the merged entity and translating the new Truist brand into a design system deployed across all digital products.</p>
      </div>
      <div>
        <div class="meta-grid">
          <div class="meta-item">
            <h4>My Role</h4>
            <p>Head of UX Design &amp; Research</p>
          </div>
          <div class="meta-item">
            <h4>Company</h4>
            <p>SunTrust → Truist Financial</p>
          </div>
          <div class="meta-item">
            <h4>Scope</h4>
            <p>All lines of business (SunTrust); Business &amp; Commercial Banking (Truist); Design System</p>
          </div>
          <div class="meta-item">
            <h4>Team</h4>
            <p>UX/UI Designers, Researchers, Product Managers, Engineering</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Ecosystem -->
  <div class="ecosystem">
    <div class="section-label">The Ecosystem</div>
    <h2 class="section-heading">One design language across every surface.</h2>
    <p class="section-body">At SunTrust, I owned every digital touchpoint — consumer mobile, business banking, and the web platform. That breadth meant the design system had to hold together across radically different use cases and user needs.</p>

    <div class="ecosystem-grid">
      <div class="eco-card">
        <img src="/images/truist/1771246123096-e2ad64a0.png" alt="Truist mobile home screen">
        <div class="eco-card-text">
          <h3>Consumer Mobile</h3>
          <p>Account management, transfers, and day-to-day banking designed for speed and clarity.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="eco-card">
        <img src="/images/truist/f6b34fae57ddb0e3fc45c70cca0e5130.webp" alt="Truist business banking dashboard">
        <div class="eco-card-text">
          <h3>Business Banking</h3>
          <p>Multi-account management, notifications, and commercial tools for business clients.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="eco-card">
        <img src="/images/truist/1771246117084-2367c12e.png" alt="Truist dashboard on laptop">
        <div class="eco-card-text">
          <h3>Web Platform</h3>
          <p>Full-featured dashboard with spending analytics, account activity, and cross-product visibility.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- Dark Showcase: App Depth -->
  <div class="showcase-dark">
    <div class="section-label">Going Deeper</div>
    <h2 class="section-heading">The details that make banking feel effortless.</h2>
    <p class="section-body">Every flow — from transferring money to verifying your identity — was designed to reduce friction and build confidence.</p>

    <div class="showcase-row">
      <div class="showcase-card">
        <img src="/images/truist/1771281467064-e8609008.png" alt="Truist app interaction flows">
        <div class="showcase-card-text">
          <h3>Core Interaction Flows</h3>
          <p>Transfers, chat, and confirmations — designed as a system, not screens.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="showcase-card">
        <img src="/images/truist/1771281469482-048153c4.png" alt="Truist cross-device payments">
        <div class="showcase-card-text">
          <h3>Cross-Device Payments</h3>
          <p>Transfers and QR payments across mobile, web, and wearables.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="showcase-row" style="margin-top: 48px;">
      <div class="showcase-card">
        <img src="/images/truist/1771281472014-694a3592.png" alt="Truist biometric security">
        <div class="showcase-card-text">
          <h3>Biometric Security</h3>
          <p>Facial recognition and biometric authentication integrated seamlessly into the experience.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="showcase-card">
        <img src="/images/truist/1771246115132-cd678175.png" alt="Truist responsive design system">
        <div class="showcase-card-text">
          <h3>Responsive Design System</h3>
          <p>Consistent brand expression from mobile to desktop to tablet.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- Onboarding Feature -->
  <div class="feature-row">
    <div class="feature-image">
      <img src="/images/truist/1771281481615-23cda954.jpg" alt="Truist onboarding flow on laptop">
    </div>
    <div class="feature-text">
      <div class="section-label">Onboarding</div>
      <h2 class="section-heading">First impressions, done right.</h2>
      <p class="section-body">Opening an account is the first real relationship moment. I pushed the team to treat onboarding not as a form, but as a conversation — progressive disclosure, clear progress, and a sense that the bank actually cares about getting to know you.</p>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- Wealth Management -->
  <section class="wealth">
    <div class="section-label">Wealth Management</div>
    <h2 class="section-heading">Designing for the highest-value clients.</h2>
    <p class="section-body">The wealth management platform required a different register — sophisticated, information-dense, and built for clients managing substantial portfolios. The same design system, elevated for a different audience.</p>
    <div class="wealth-hero-img">
      <img src="/images/truist/original.png" alt="Truist wealth management dashboard">
    </div>
  </section>

</CaseStudyLayout>
